Class FilterQueryParam

Direct Known Subclasses:
FilterByFieldQueryParam, FilterByLineQueryParam
public abstract class FilterQueryParam
extends QueryParam

This is an abstract class provides the ability to submit filter searches with a VdrSearchExpression search expression that contains search terms joined by either AND or OR search conjunction operators.

The concrete filter query param classes are:

  • FilterByFieldQueryParam
  • FilterByLineQueryParam
